Package: workspace-switcher
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libxpm4, libxrandr2
Description:  Workspace switching utility for X11
 workspace-switcher allows users to switch between multiple X11 workspaces easily.
 It provides a graphical interface for managing workspaces,
 supporting various configurations.
